d by the same case study, it is easy to compare and evaluate the results. The statements in the text are further consolidated by abstracts and evaluations of each of the methods. Exercises with extensive solutions will lead to the confidence which is necessary for an ease of handling the investment appraisal techniques and for a good preparation for students’ exams. German and international students at universities and other institutions of higher education will find this book an excellent systematic preparation for their exams.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aBusiness enterprisesxFinance. 0aCorporationsxFinance. 0aInvestment analysis. 0aInvestments. 4aDiscounting Methods. 4aInvestment Decision. 4aNon-discounting Methods. 4aUncertainty. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Finance / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Business and Economics 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062114308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Business and Economics 2000 - 2014z9783110635737oZDB-23-GBE08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Business 2014z9783110369649oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831103971920 cprintz978311034718040uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978311034719740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110347197423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110347197/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-062114-3  DGBA Backlist Business and Economics 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EB